To compile the file locally (see also ../../bin/compile.sh):

- html:
 pandoc -t html5 --toc -s -S -V toctitle:'Table of content' -o Ruggedpodinstallationguide.html Ruggedpodinstallationguide.md

- pdf:
 TODO (images should be in the repository rather than in /usr/share/wordpress/?)
 1. scp -r <login>@ruggedpod.qyshare.com:/usr/share/wordpress/Webdav/Public/ruggedpod_usermanual/pictures ./
 2. sed 's!http://ruggedpod.qyshare.com/Webdav/Public/ruggedpod_usermanual/pictures/!./pictures/!' Ruggedpodinstallationguide.md > Ruggedpodinstallationguide-local.md
 3. pandoc -t latex --latex-engine=xelatex --toc -s -S -V toctitle:'Table of content' -o Ruggedpodinstallationguide-local.pdf Ruggedpodinstallationguide-local.md
